OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPatchy low
OL,6,Fcloud will return into the evening,
OL,7,Fwith areas of mist and fog developing
OL,8,Flater in the night. Chilly, with an
OL,9,Fisolated frost likely as winds fall
OL,10,Flight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FEarly low cloud, mist and
OL,13,Ffog soon clearing to give another fine
OL,14,Fand dry day with long sunny spells and
OL,15,Flight winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,18,Ffine and warm during this period with
OL,19,Fplenty of sunny spells and light
OL,20,Fwinds. Chilly at times overnight with
OL,21,Fsome patchy overnight fog possible.
